pasti akan dipecat.

347
00:23:32,119 --> 00:23:34,119
Jika bukan sengaja
mencelakai, apa lagi?

348
00:23:35,199 --> 00:23:36,079
Dipecat?

349
00:23:40,439 --> 00:23:41,760
